                    <span>This is an absolutely incredible book.  I bought it as a required textbook for a graduate course. I was somewhat skeptical when the professor said that previous students ended up buying several copies of the book to give as Christmas presents.  But she was right!  The book is truly transformational, not only in how you can resolve current issues but in helping analyze what happened in the past.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great resource for coaches</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
